name: Somnio Software

Let’s create successful Flutter apps together!

name: Code Magic
about: Codemagic - your friendly CI/CD for Flutter developers. Automatically build, test and deliver mobile apps in record time. All platforms. Great docs.

name: atSign
about: Atsign is a community of Internet optimists compelled by the belief that privacy is a fundamental right. We created the open-source atPlatform so developers can build decentralized apps that do not rely on blockchain. The atPlatform is written in Dart and all the apps are developed with Flutter. On the atPlatform, data is cryptographically signed and end-to-end encrypted between mutually authenticated endpoints. For IoT devices, the atPlatform eliminates the complexity and cost of VPNs and firewall infrastructure while actually increasing security. All atPlatform apps are accessed via a unique identification and authentication approach: the atSign — the key for people to reclaim their power online.

name: Superlist
about: Superlist is the next generation productivity tool for individuals and teams alike. With Superlist you and your team can plan, collaborate, and get it all done - and feel good about it. Available on all major platforms, Superlist will accompany you and be there for you whenever you need it, helping you stay on top of everything you need to keep track of.

name: Tide
about: Tide is a financial platform which helps SMEs save time (and money) in the running of their businesses by not only offering business accounts and related banking services, but also a comprehensive set of highly usable administrative solutions. In other words - The Tide app helps streamline processes such as invoicing, expense management, accounting and payroll  through automation, and smart, intuitive tools. The needs of SMEs globally are largely universal, with time wasted on business and administrative tasks being a key issue. Tide exists to fix that problem. Tide has developed the right approach and a mix of services to meet the diverse needs of small businesses. Specific projects include a global transition to Flutter, creating an innovative proposition in the Open Banking space, managing multiple migrations to continuously improve the user experience, as well as building and improving Tide products each day. Tide is currently a big player in the UK business banking market on its way to scale globally. The headquarters of the company are located in London. The core divisions are based in Sofia, Bulgaria and in Hyderabad, India.
